OL,3,CWatchdog lifts restrictions on
OL,4,Chospital trust after being downgraded
OL,6,FA health watchdog has lifted
OL,7,Frestrictions imposed on a North East
OL,8,Fhospital trust that was downgraded
OL,9,Fearlier this year.
OL,11,FThe Newcastle upon Tyne Hospitals NHS
OL,12,FFoundation Trust saw its rating fall
OL,13,Ffrom 'outstanding' to 'requires
OL,14,Fimprovement', following a Care Quality
OL,15,FCommission (CQC) report which outlined
OL,16,Fserious concerns over alleged bullying
OL,17,Fand a "significant deterioration" in
OL,18,Fthe leadership.
