OL,3,CWatchdog lifts restrictions on
OL,4,Chospital trust after being downgraded
OL,6,FThe trust, which runs the Royal
OL,7,FVictoria Infirmary and the Freeman
OL,8,FHospital, also had a series of
OL,9,Fconditions imposed on its licence to
OL,10,Fprovide services by the CQC `
OL,11,Frequiring it to make certain
OL,12,Fimprovements and submit monthly
OL,13,Freports to prove it was making
OL,14,Fprogress.
OL,16,FThose requirements have now been
OL,17,Flifted after the watchdog was
OL,18,Fsatisfied that sufficient improvements
OL,19,Fhave been made over the course of this
OL,20,Fyear, the Local Democracy Reporting
OL,21,FService said.
