OL,3,CWatchdog lifts restrictions on
OL,4,Chospital trust after being downgraded
OL,6,FThe CQC said it would "continue to
OL,7,Fmonitor the trust closely".
OL,9,FIn a statement, A CQC spokesperson
OL,10,Fsaid: "Following an inspection at The
OL,11,FNewcastle upon Tyne Hospitals NHS
OL,12,FFoundation Trust last year, CQC placed
OL,13,Fconditions on the trust's registration
OL,14,Fdue to a number of concerns found.
OL,16,F"These conditions required the trust
OL,17,Fto make specific improvements within a
OL,18,Fspecified timescale and to submit
OL,19,Fmonthly reports to CQC showing
OL,20,Fprogress, and action taken to improve
OL,21,Fquality and safety.
