OL,6,F"CQC's priority, at all times, is the
OL,7,Fhealth and wellbeing of people using
OL,8,Fhealth and social care services, and
OL,9,Fall information we receive informs our
OL,10,Fmonitoring of services and future
OL,11,Finspections. If we're not satisfied
OL,12,Fpeople are receiving safe care, we
OL,13,Fwill not hesitate to take action in
OL,14,Fline with our regulatory powers.
