OL,3,CWatchdog lifts restrictions on
OL,4,Chospital trust after being downgraded
OL,6,FThe CQC inspection report published in
OL,7,FJanuary this year condemned a
OL,8,F"significant deterioration" in
OL,9,Fleadership at the hospitals, which had
OL,10,Fpreviously been considered among the
OL,11,Fworld's best.
OL,13,FInspectors highlighted particular
OL,14,Fconcern over the Freeman's
OL,15,Fcardiothoracic department, with claims
OL,16,Fof serious incidents being
OL,17,F"deliberately covered up" and a
OL,18,Fculture of bullying.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@[O]yD@AOUyD@YO]
