OL,4,Chospital trust after being downgraded
OL,6,FThe findings also included worries
OL,7,Fabout a shortage of staffing in the
OL,8,FRVI's maternity unit, which left it
OL,9,Funable to provide "basic fundamental
OL,10,Fstandards of care", as well as
OL,11,Faccusations of favouritism and
OL,12,Fnepotism within the trust.
